[SPEAKER_04] Niste vi sami sebi prepisali, nego su sad ovi drugi vas prepisali.

254
00:21:07,599 --> 00:21:09,599
[SPEAKER_04] Pa to tako ide, da ste.

255
00:21:09,599 --> 00:21:19,599
