00:23:02,599 --> 00:23:03,599
[SPEAKER_03] Mislim...

286
00:23:03,599 --> 00:23:05,599
[SPEAKER_04] Malo, malo mi izgleda da je skepsa prema tome,

287
00:23:05,599 --> 00:23:06,599
[SPEAKER_04] gomilanje funkcije.

288
00:23:06,599 --> 00:23:08,599
[SPEAKER_04] Vaš problem nije u tome...

289
00:23:08,599 --> 00:23:10,599
[SPEAKER_04] Program je super izgleda,

290
00:23:10,599 --> 00:23:12,599
[SPEAKER_05] ali nije to vaš problem.

291
00:23:12,599 --> 00:23:13,599
[SPEAKER_05] Problem je što se ljudi pitaju,

292
00:23:13,599 --> 00:23:15,599
[SPEAKER_05] pa hoće li ti ljudi stvarno to napraviti.

293
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:16,599
[SPEAKER_05] Mislim, to je pitanje.

294
00:23:16,599 --> 00:23:17,599
[SPEAKER_05] To je pitanje...

295
00:23:17,599 --> 00:23:18,599
[SPEAKER_05] Koji ljudi?

296
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:19,599
[SPEAKER_03] Pa...

297
00:23:19,599 --> 00:23:21,599
[SPEAKER_03] Zašto vi ne bi sudjelovili u tome,

298
00:23:21,599 --> 00:23:22,599
[SPEAKER_03] u izvođenju tog programa?

299
00:23:22,599 --> 00:23:25,599
[SPEAKER_03] Zašto ovi ljudi koji tu sjedili nas gledaju u tome...

300
00:23:25,599 --> 00:23:27,599
[SPEAKER_03] Ja se vraćam na onu tezu,

301
00:23:27,599 --> 00:23:29,599
[SPEAKER_03] dakle, imamo izbore za Sabor.

302
00:23:29,599 --> 00:23:31,599
[SPEAKER_03] U Saboru će se formirati,

303
00:23:31,599 --> 00:23:32,599
[SPEAKER_03] ja se nadam,

304
00:23:32,599 --> 00:23:34,599
[SPEAKER_03] vladovića većina vrlo brzo nakon izbora,

305
00:23:34,599 --> 00:23:35,599
[SPEAKER_03] koja će reći:

306
00:23:35,599 --> 00:23:36,599
[SPEAKER_03] ti, ti ili ti ćeš,

307
00:23:36,599 --> 00:23:38,599
[SPEAKER_03] evo, tebi ću potpisati,

308
00:23:38,599 --> 00:23:40,599
[SPEAKER_03] odi gore kod Milanovića po mandatu,

309
00:23:40,599 --> 00:23:42,599
[SPEAKER_03] i formiraj vladu.

310
00:23:42,599 --> 00:23:43,599
[SPEAKER_03] A nakon toga,

311
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,599
[SPEAKER_03] za to što želimo,

312
00:23:44,599 --> 00:23:46,599
[SPEAKER_03] a to nije sada reforma,

313
00:23:46,599 --> 00:23:48,599
[SPEAKER_03] to nije kozmetičke promjene,

314
00:23:48,599 --> 00:23:52,599
[SPEAKER_03] da pomaknemo ministarstvo s lijevog na desnog,

315
00:23:52,599 --> 00:23:54,599
[SPEAKER_03] ili da spojimo ured sa ministarstvom,

316
00:23:54,599 --> 00:23:55,599
[SPEAKER_03] pa ćemo promijeliti tabu.

317
00:23:55,599 --> 00:23:59,599
[SPEAKER_03] Ovo je trenutak u kojem se treba dogoditi transformativni procesi.

318
00:23:59,599 --> 00:24:01,599
[SPEAKER_03] Za transformativne procese,

319
00:24:01,599 --> 00:24:04,599
[SPEAKER_03] oni koji znaju upravljanje promjenama,

320
00:24:04,599 --> 00:24:05,599
[SPEAKER_03] change management,

321
00:24:05,599 --> 00:24:07,599
[SPEAKER_03] znaju kako se to radi.

322
00:24:07,599 --> 00:24:09,599
[SPEAKER_03] U tome trebate imati prvo tim koji to radi,

323
00:24:09,599 --> 00:24:11,599
[SPEAKER_03] trebate imati zajedničku ideju,

324
00:24:11,599 --> 00:24:13,599
[SPEAKER_03] i trebate i za to nije dovoljna vlada.

325
00:24:13,599 --> 00:24:17,599
[SPEAKER_05] Ne, ali mi poduzetnici točno znamo šta su ti procesi.

326
00:24:17,599 --> 00:24:19,599
[SPEAKER_05] Biće ovoga, samo se čuje miso,

327
00:24:19,599 --> 00:24:21,599
[SPEAKER_04] ali brzo vidim vime.

328
00:24:21,599 --> 00:24:24,599
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, neće vlada to moći sama napraviti.

329
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:27,599
[SPEAKER_03] Vlada, ministri, premijeri, nisu čarobnjaci.

330
00:24:27,599 --> 00:24:30,599
[SPEAKER_05] Vaš problem nije napisati dobar program,

331
00:24:30,599 --> 00:24:34,599
[SPEAKER_05] nego vaš problem u tome što u Hrvatskoj,

332
00:24:34,599 --> 00:24:36,599
[SPEAKER_05] mi u Hrvatskoj znamo šta treba napraviti.

333
00:24:36,599 --> 00:24:38,599
[SPEAKER_04] Super, idemo pogledati šta nam poručuju,

334
00:24:38,599 --> 00:24:41,599
[SPEAKER_04] naši sponzori i onda poslušati malo klapu Kampanel,

335
00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:43,599
[SPEAKER_04] a onda sačuvajmo ove misli.

336
00:24:43,599 --> 00:24:44,599
[SPEAKER_04] Dakle, imamo vremena.

337
00:24:44,599 --> 00:24:46,599
[SPEAKER_04] Sve ćemo ovo miras bistriti u nastavku.

338
00:24:46,599 --> 00:24:48,599
[SPEAKER_04] Dakle, prvo spot od sponzora,

339
00:24:48,599 --> 00:24:50,599
[SPEAKER_04] a onda nakon toga i još jednom klapa Kampanel.

340
00:24:50,599 --> 00:24:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] Opremi i uljepšaj svoj balkon, vrt ili terasu u Emeceti.

